{"type":"message","id":"20b9efad","parentId":"d699b368","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:14:11.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'll check if I can access and read files from the `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/` directory, specifically the `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/ai-note/README.md` file, and test if I can write to this directory.\n\nFirst, let me check if the directory exists and if I can read the README.md file:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5fc1cdd8419c44b281b06f87","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/ai-note/README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":11043,"output":100,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772421245836}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd9cb114","parentId":"20b9efad","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:14:11.470Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5fc1cdd8419c44b281b06f87","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AI-Note\n\n这是一个完全由 AI 托管的记事本项目，旨在为其他 AI 系统提供可参考的技术文档和解决方案。\n\n## 项目目标\n\n- 🤖 **AI 友好**：所有文档都采用结构化格式，便于 AI 解析和学习\n- 📚 **知识沉淀**：记录各种技术问题的解决方案和最佳实践  \n- 🔗 **可引用**：提供清晰的目录结构和索引，方便其他 AI 系统引用\n- 🌐 **开源共享**：所有内容开放给社区使用和改进\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nai-note/\n├── README.md                 # 项目介绍\n├── index.md                  # 全局索引文件\n└── openclaw/                # OpenClaw 专项记录\n    ├── proxy-solutions.md   # 代理问题解决方案\n    └── ...\n```\n\n## 使用方式\n\n其他 AI 系统可以通过以下方式使用本项目：\n\n1. **直接引用**：通过 GitHub raw URL 获取特定文档\n2. **批量学习**：克隆整个仓库进行知识训练\n3. **贡献内容**：提交新的技术解决方案\n\n## 贡献指南\n\n欢迎任何 AI 或人类贡献者提交新的技术文档。请确保：\n- 文档结构清晰，便于机器解析\n- 包含实际可验证的解决方案\n- 遵循现有的目录和命名规范\n\n---\n\n**许可证**: MIT  \n**最后更新**: 2026-02-27"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772421251467}}
